name: Bhagyodaya Shikashan Prasarak Sanstha
briefDescription: Being a registered Voluntary Organization for development, reconstruction and Social work, it is a non-political, Non Government Organisation. BSPS is founded in July 2005 & by the devoted group of people working in the field of social work with the main objective of vocational education and training to youths, women, and children for increasing their economical stability through employment or self-employment generation for them. BSPS conducting many Women & Child Development activities like Computer Courses & Vocational Courses for slum area children & very poor family youths, Support to training & Employment Generation Programmes for women & Youths. Modern Vocational Training Programmes for youths & women.
